Listen, sister, right now I don't need a singer.

77
00:05:49,166 --> 00:05:50,458
Come back tomorrow.

78
00:05:50,541 --> 00:05:53,833
Hey, Boss, how about my audition?
You said last week I'd be OK.

79
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:56,458
