89
00:06:33,916 --> 00:06:38,125
Don't worry, babe. I've been trying to see him
for months and months and months.

90
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:40,041
- You have?
- Of course I have.

91
00:06:40,125 --> 00:06:41,291
