622
00:41:07,041 --> 00:41:09,125
# I'm feeling fine

623
00:41:10,375 --> 00:41:13,458
# Filled with emotions

624
00:41:13,541 --> 00:41:16,625
# Stronger than wine

625
00:41:16,708 --> 00:41:19,375
# They give me the notion

626
00:41:19,458 --> 00:41:23,291
