706
00:46:11,291 --> 00:46:13,333
Monday, 11 am.

707
00:46:13,416 --> 00:46:15,041
Right. I'll be there.

708
00:46:15,125 --> 00:46:17,000
Got him, the knucklehead.

709
00:46:17,083 --> 00:46:19,125
Got him, the salami.

710
00:46:19,208 --> 00:46:22,083
OK, Knuckles, let's go and enjoy the show.

